      "author": "sharkello",
      "description": "## Bug fix\n\n**Pull from Notion: quote blocks inside list items no longer show as blockquotes in Obsidian.**\n\nNotion stores indented text under bullet points as `quote` blocks. Previously these were converted to `>` markdown blockquotes, which Obsidian renders with a prominent left border — looking nothing like the original Notion layout. Now such blocks render as plain indented text, matching Notion's visual appearance.",
